{"success":true,"payload":{"value":{"id":"150489064c30","versionId":"dc87825e1b1d","creatorId":"4a41236ee91e","homeCollectionId":"23738d481ce8","title":"Dart in Google Summer of Code 2026","detectedLanguage":"en","latestVersion":"dc87825e1b1d","latestPublishedVersion":"dc87825e1b1d","hasUnpublishedEdits":false,"latestRev":60,"createdAt":1772195175461,"updatedAt":1772739743455,"acceptedAt":0,"firstPublishedAt":1772733925054,"latestPublishedAt":1772733925054,"vote":false,"experimentalCss":"","displayAuthor":"","content":{"subtitle":"We’re excited to announce that the Dart project will mentor contributors for the seventh time in Google Summer of Code 2026!","bodyModel":{"paragraphs":[{"name":"9abb","type":3,"text":"Dart in Google Summer of Code 2026","markups":[]},{"name":"518e","type":1,"text":"We’re excited to announce that the Dart project will mentor contributors for the seventh time in Google Summer of Code 2026!","markups":[]},{"name":"ed94","type":4,"text":"","markups":[],"layout":1,"metadata":{"id":"1*iPTqUuppL1UCAJ8OWAcWhg.png","originalWidth":1920,"originalHeight":1080}},{"name":"dc3a","type":1,"text":"The Google Summer of Code (GSoC) program focuses on bringing student developers from around the world into open source software development. Google sponsors students to work with a mentoring open source organization on a 12-week (or longer) programming project during the summer. Over the past 21 years, more than 22,000 contributors have participated in Google Summer of Code.","markups":[{"type":3,"start":4,"end":25,"href":"https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/","title":"","rel":"","anchorType":0}]},{"name":"ac04","type":1,"text":"Are you interested?","markups":[{"type":1,"start":0,"end":19}]},{"name":"3228","type":1,"text":"To get started now, read the list of project ideas to find a match for your skills and interests. Formal applications must be submitted before March 31st. We encourage prospective applicants to submit early drafts and ask for feedback.","markups":[{"type":3,"start":25,"end":50,"href":"https://github.com/dart-lang/sdk/blob/main/docs/gsoc/Dart-GSoC-2026-Project-Ideas.md","title":"","rel":"","anchorType":0}]},{"name":"200d","type":1,"text":"The Dart team expects to have enough mentors to accept only a small number of applications, so we encourage you to review other mentoring organizations as well.","markups":[{"type":3,"start":128,"end":151,"href":"https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2026/organizations","title":"","rel":"","anchorType":0},{"type":2,"start":0,"end":160}]},{"name":"2a6c","type":1,"text":"If you have questions specific to Dart and GSoC, ask them on our dedicated mailing list.","markups":[{"type":3,"start":61,"end":87,"href":"https://groups.google.com/g/dart-gsoc","title":"","rel":"","anchorType":0}]},{"name":"9d74","type":1,"text":"To learn more about Google Summer of Code, watch the following video or read the contributor guide for Google Summer of Code.","markups":[{"type":3,"start":77,"end":124,"href":"https://google.github.io/gsocguides/student/","title":"","rel":"","anchorType":0}]},{"name":"6949","type":11,"text":"","markups":[],"layout":1,"iframe":{"mediaResourceId":"2f7a6111e84d69cfd8478327d937df69","iframeWidth":854,"iframeHeight":480,"thumbnailUrl":"https://i.embed.ly/1/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FS6IP_6HG2QE%2Fhqdefault.jpg&key=a19fcc184b9711e1b4764040d3dc5c07"}},{"name":"b174","type":1,"text":"We look forward to hearing from you!","markups":[]}],"sections":[{"name":"1042","startIndex":0}]},"postDisplay":{"coverless":true}},"virtuals":{"statusForCollection":"APPROVED","allowNotes":true,"previewImage":{"imageId":"1*iPTqUuppL1UCAJ8OWAcWhg.png","filter":"","backgroundSize":"","originalWidth":1920,"originalHeight":1080,"strategy":"resample","height":0,"width":0},"wordCount":201,"imageCount":1,"readingTime":0.9584905660377359,"subtitle":"We’re excited to announce that the Dart project will mentor contributors for the seventh time in Google Summer of Code 2026!",